{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b Fazenda do Franc\u234 ?s - Regenerative Guest House} {\i Cachoeiras de Macacu, RJ - 120km from Rio de Janeiro}\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b RECONNECT with nature}\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 We are a family farm with over 40 years of history, where French tradition meets the exuberance of the Atlantic Forest. We are looking for people passionate about nature, sustainability, and rural life to help us build a regenerative space.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b What we offer:} - Comfortable room in a family environment - 3 meals daily with authentic French cuisine - Access to all activities: trails, pool, forest bathing - Immersive experience in permaculture and hospitality - Fiber optic WiFi - Welcoming atmosphere with mountain views\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b What we\u8217're looking for:} - People interested in organic farming, permaculture, or hospitality - Availability for 4-5 hours of work/day (5 days/week) - Collaborative spirit and respect for nature - Minimum stay of 2 weeks (ideal: 1 month)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b Possible activities:} - Caring for the vegetable garden and gardens - Helping with breakfast and kitchen duties - Animal care (horses, cows) - General maintenance support - Creating content for social media\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b About us:} Our farm was founded by Erick Lanthiez, a French farmer who brought family recipes and a love for the land. Today, in the third generation, we offer a unique regenerative hospitality experience.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b Location:} - 120km from Rio de Janeiro (1.5 hours by car) - Cachoeiras de Macacu region - Neighbors to the Guapia\u231 ?u Ecological Reserve (REGUA)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b Contact:} WhatsApp: +55 21 97920-1646 Instagram: @fazendadofrances Email: fazendadofrances@gmail.com\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\i Come be part of our family and discover the true meaning of reconnection.}\par}
